      <title>金胡萝卜会员计划</title>
      <link href="/goldvip.html"/>
      <url>/goldvip.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h1><p>MIDI包以压缩包的形式进行分享，压缩包内包含：</p><ol><li>伴奏</li><li>提取的干声</li><li>.mid文件</li></ol><p>适合ACE studio、utau等调音软件使用。目前已更新200+首，持续更新中！</p><hr><h1 id="会员计划有哪些midi？"><a href="#会员计划有哪些midi？" class="headerlink" title="会员计划有哪些midi？"></a>会员计划有哪些midi？</h1><p>会员计划目前已更新 <wavy>200+</wavy> </p><div calss='anzhiyu-tag-link'><a class="tag-Link" target="_blank" href="https://kdocs.cn/l/csKZhd7ObH6b">    <div class="tag-link-tips">引用站外地址</div>    <div class="tag-link-bottom">        <div class="tag-link-left" style="">          <i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-link" style=""></i>        </div>        <div class="tag-link-right">            <div class="tag-link-title">金山表格</div>            <div class="tag-link-sitename">立即金胡萝卜会员专属MIDI包表 </div>        </div>        <i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-angle-right"></i>    </div>    </a></div><h3 id="更新日志"><a href="#更新日志" class="headerlink" title="更新日志"></a>更新日志</h3><div class="timeline orange"><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2024</p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>07-06</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>更新 66 首 共 238 首</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>03-06</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>更新 15 首 共 172 首</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>02-17</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>更新 23 首 共 157 首</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>01-12</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>更新 7 首 共134 首</p></div></div></div><hr><h1 id="会员计划的定价"><a href="#会员计划的定价" class="headerlink" title="会员计划的定价"></a>会员计划的定价</h1><p>金胡萝卜会员价为： <u>￥49.8 元/永久更新</u> &#x3D; <u>25元×N</u> 的midi伴奏包 + <u>399元/年</u> 的包图网会员 + 后续更多服务</p><p>随着MIDI量的增多，会员价会逐渐上调</p><div calss='anzhiyu-tag-link'><a class="tag-Link" target="_blank" href="https://ifdian.net/a/HLBXE">    <div class="tag-link-tips">引用站外地址</div>    <div class="tag-link-bottom">        <div class="tag-link-left" style="background-image: url(https://static.afdiancdn.com/static/img/logo/logo.png)">          <i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-link" style="display: none"></i>        </div>        <div class="tag-link-right">            <div class="tag-link-title">爱发电</div>            <div class="tag-link-sitename">立即去爱发电订阅金胡萝卜会员 </div>        </div>        <i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-angle-right"></i>    </div>    </a></div>]]></content>
      
      
